      instruction: 'It looks like this centrifuge is imbalanced. An unbalanced centrifuge
        can shake violently, causing mechanical failure, sample spillage, or even
        breakage. This can lead to contamination, equipment damage, and injury from
        flying debris. Click it to see it balanced. '
