    - stepName: CleanWithRag
      narrationClip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 58ada2cde9b92374fad40fc952272133, type: 3}
      instruction: 'Now that the acid has been neutralized, it can be safely wiped
        up with an absorbent pad. '
      actionComplete: 0
      actionType: 0
      targetObject: {fileID: 0}
      customActionEvent:
        m_PersistentCalls:
          m_Calls: []
      postActions: []
    - stepName: ChemicalWasteBin
      narrationClip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 7396e3e012c9d544da4a1ac997646b88, type: 3}
      instruction: Since the absorbent pad and your gloves are contaminated with
        chemical waste, they must be disposed of in the chemical waste bin.
      actionComplete: 0
      actionType: 1
      targetObject: {fileID: 0}
      customActionEvent:
        m_PersistentCalls:
          m_Calls: []
      postActions: []
    - stepName: WashHandsAfterSpill
      narrationClip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: aed0ebdd5c79a3846a4accedb26c6cdd, type: 3}
      instruction: Magnificent! We've successfully cleaned up a spill! Return to
        the sink to re-wash your hands.
      actionComplete: 0
      actionType: 1
      targetObject: {fileID: 0}
      customActionEvent:
        m_PersistentCalls:
          m_Calls: []
      postActions: []
